dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings in fathoms. Shows roads, canals, aqueducts, oil pipelines, glaciers, and national parks. Lower left margin: "02297" Produced by the Cartographic Division. "Information contributed by Touring Club Italiano."
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : National Geographic Society. Cartographic Division, 2010.
